{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781203314188,"sessionID":"ses_14814a23bffel8UYRQn6odJS7g","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_6zs4229y","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"README.md","content":"# Temperature Conversion CLI Tool\n\n## Installation\n\nInstall the package using pip:\n\npip install temperature-converter\n\n## Usage\n\nConvert Celsius to Fahrenheit:\ntemperature-converter celsius fahrenheit 25\n\nConvert Fahrenheit to Celsius:\ntemperature-converter fahrenheit celsius 77\n\nConvert Celsius to Kelvin:\ntemperature-converter celsius kelvin 300\n\n## Supported Conversions\n\n- Celsius to Fahrenheit\n- Fahrenheit to Celsius\n- Celsius to Kelvin"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/nathangreen/Development/eddi-lab/llm-orc/scratch/spike-pi-form-adequacy-gate/B_smoke3/ws_1/README.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"scratch/spike-pi-form-adequacy-gate/B_smoke3/ws_1/README.md","time":{"start":1781203313429,"end":1781203314144}},"id":"prt_eb7fda061001WkuaxmOnelntaD","sessionID":"ses_14814a23bffel8UYRQn6odJS7g","messageID":"msg_eb7f9d89e0011hV36ZtOZaFXZl"}}
